<!-- venv\Scripts\activate to activate venv -->

Why not basic Flask?
Because:

* You want real-time events
* You want multiple rooms
* You want structured models
* You want maintainable architecture

Use:

* WebSockets for real-time updates
* REST endpoints for structured actions
* Database for persistence

