## Frontend (Players & Host)

Modern frontend (ideal approach):

* React
  or
* Next.js

This gives:

* Dynamic UI
* Real-time updates
* Clean role-based interfaces
* Separate host vs player views

You could start simple, but architect it as if it’s scalable.

